/>\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會，陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾；Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.12 @Template End@"},{"pid":"402559e42aeb3bfb3e6fe2cfb32ca973beb15f3a","tid":1562700,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:46:44.000Z","msg":"人地個人權法係講緊美國自己點做，關你港共政府咩事，美國內政唔到你說三道四<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cff84903d5a1790c801d0f8d1ab9e2f240f694d","tid":1562700,"uid":286374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:48:10.000Z","msg":"夠薑就直接叫美國取消啦"},{"pid":"4190386c0242f38166af576d8a999a768ad91056","tid":1562700,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:48:21.000Z","msg":"想做特首？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1806e5810ded8583eb778893468504ef4a7dea74","tid":1562700,"uid":169665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:48:24.000Z","msg":"佢痴Q左線呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3356913c1b787c771c469f7b8c19ccddba32b707","tid":1562700,"uid":259493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:48:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港只有 兩條出路 ~<br />\n增加美國支持，法案審議中，我們必須做好英文文宣，寄給國會議員！普選和永遠廢除中聯辦；<br />\n和被壓迫的内地人一起反抗~反宣傳大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 再冇其他選擇 香港人不講獨立不分化<br />\n  一齊頂硬上！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"967268e8ed99f79d9abdc2cb9b7b920d87cd1d5d","tid":1562700,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1ec7a1648caa894499063ff0a77caf8cb40f600","tid":1562700,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:48:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov